          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "良好的溝通能力對跨國公司的任何經理來說都是不可或缺的。"
          }
        },
        {
          "en": "Water, food, and shelter are considered the most essential needs for disaster relief.",
          "highlight": [
            "most essential"
          ],
          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "水、食物和住所被視為災難救援中最迫切的必需品。"
          }
        },
        {
          "en": "The manual covers the essentials of workplace safety in just twenty pages.",
          "highlight": [
            "essentials"
          ],
          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "這本手冊只用了二十頁就涵蓋了職場安全的要點。"
          }
        }
